A EGGS BENEDICT.

14:08.950 --> 14:11.327
- WELL, HE IS
IN A LOVELY MOOD.

14:11.430 --> 14:13.045
- YOU KNOW, SON,
I GOTTA TELL YOU SOMETHING.

14:13.160 --> 14:15.367
