WHOLE FAMILY NOT BEING HERE.

14:15.470 --> 14:17.119
- OH, GOD, DAD, YOU YOU MIND?
I'M A LITTLE BUSY BACK HERE.

14:17.230 --> 14:18.265
- NO, I UNDERSTAND,
YOU KNOW,

14:18.370 --> 14:20.600
