SO LET'S JUST DROP IT, OKAY?

14:31.140 --> 14:32.129
- WELL, TELL ME SOMETHING,
ADAM.

14:32.250 --> 14:33.103
DID THE BABY
DO ANYTHING?

14:33.210 --> 14:34.177
'CAUSE HOW COME THE BABY
CAN'T BE HERE?

