IS THE CHAIR?

16:43.140 --> 16:44.858
I TOLD YOU TO KEEP YOUR EYES
ON IT, AND IT'S GONE!

16:44.960 --> 16:48.236
- I LOOKED AT MY MENU
AND IT WAS GONE!

16:48.350 --> 16:51.558
THEY COULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN FAR.
IT'S A 600-POUND RECLINER.

16:51.660 --> 16:52.797
- THIS IS NOT FUNNY!

16:52.900 --> 16:56.210
[overlapping chatter
and laughter]

17:01.220 --> 17:02.084
- BOY, I CAN'T BELIEVE
SHE'S MAKING ME

17:02.190 --> 17:03.327
