17:07.370 --> 17:11.261
HAVE TO SEE HER HAVING SEX
WITH MR. CYR.

17:11.370 --> 17:12.439
YEAH.
- YOU'RE NOT SERIOUS.

17:12.540 --> 17:13.643
- ABSOLUTELY, YES.
I'M DEAD SERIOUS.

17:13.750 --> 17:15.365
- OH, MY GOD.
NO.

17:15.480 --> 17:16.617
- I, LIKE, WENT TO GET A CD
FROM THE GUESTHOUSE

17:16.720 --> 17:19.848
AND WALKED IN ON--YEAH.
- [gasps] NO.

17:19.960 --> 17:21.029
